  "title": "Banco de Dados — Cloud",
  "uid": "cloud-banco-de-dados",
  "version": 1,
  "weekStart": "",
  "refresh": "30s",
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Atlas — Prometheus integration pendente",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Cluster em prod: **`cluster0.xgugpph.mongodb.net`** (Atlas).\n\nPainéis abaixo ficam em `—` até habilitar o scrape de métricas Atlas. Passo-a-passo:\n\n1. **Atlas → Project Settings → Integrations → Prometheus** — habilite (free tier suporta) e copie URL/Username/Token gerados.\n2. **Adicione job ao `infra/prometheus.yml`:**\n   ```yaml\n   - job_name: mongodb-atlas\n     scrape_interval: 60s\n     scheme: https\n     basic_auth:\n       username: ${ATLAS_USER}\n       password: ${ATLAS_API_KEY}\n     metrics_path: /metrics/clusters\n     static_configs:\n       - targets: ['cloud.mongodb.com']\n   ```\n3. Recarregue: `docker compose -f infra/docker-compose.yml restart prometheus`.\n\nQueries usam `mongodb_*` (exporter padrão) `OR mongodbatlas_*` (integration nativa) — funciona em ambos."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cluster UP",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": { "text": "DOWN", "color": "red" },
                "1": { "text": "UP", "color": "green" }
              }
            }
          ],
          "noValue": "—"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "up{job=\"mongodb-atlas\"}",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true,
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Conexões",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 4, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 200 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 500 }
            ]
          },
          "noValue": "—"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "mongodb_connections{job=\"mongodb-atlas\",state=\"current\"} OR mongodbatlas_process_connections",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Operações/s (rate 5m)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 4, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["mean"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "ops", "noValue": "—" },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(mongodb_op_counters_total{job=\"mongodb-atlas\"}[5m])) OR sum(rate(mongodbatlas_process_opcounters[5m]))",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Replication lag (s)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 4, "w": 6, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 30 }
            ]
          },
          "noValue": "—"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "max(mongodb_mongod_replset_member_replication_lag_seconds{job=\"mongodb-atlas\"}) OR max(mongodbatlas_process_oplog_replication_lag_seconds)",
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Operações por tipo (rate 5m)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" },
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 8, "w": 12, "h": 9 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "ops",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 15,
            "spanNulls": false
          },
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "placement": "right",
          "showLegend": true,
          "calcs": ["mean", "max"]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "rate(mongodb_op_counters_total{job=\"mongodb-atlas\"}[5m])",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prom-cloud" }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
